  %% Diagram 58: Vendor Subscription Billing and Tier Change Flow

  Select[Vendor selects upgrade or downgrade\nFree/Starter/Growth/Pro/Enterprise]
  AuthGate{Vendor authorized for tier change?}
  Deny[Deny request and show account guidance]

  Compute[Compute billing amount\ncycle + proration]
  Attempt[Attempt payment through configured rails]
  PayResult{Payment successful?}

  Billing[(Update subscription_billing)]
  Entitlements[Apply tier entitlements]
  EntitlementCheck{Entitlements match billing state?}
  Reconcile[Run entitlement reconciliation job]
  Confirm[Return active tier confirmation]

  Grace[Enter grace period]
  Retry[Retry collection schedule]
  RetryResult{Retry successful?}
  Restrict[Restrict premium entitlements]
  Downgrade[Downgrade to safe tier policy]

  Select --> AuthGate
  AuthGate -- No --> Deny
  AuthGate -- Yes --> Compute --> Attempt --> PayResult

  PayResult -- Yes --> Billing --> Entitlements --> EntitlementCheck
  EntitlementCheck -- Yes --> Confirm
  EntitlementCheck -- No --> Reconcile --> Confirm

  PayResult -- No --> Grace --> Retry --> RetryResult
  RetryResult -- Yes --> Billing
  RetryResult -- No --> Restrict --> Downgrade
